'''Grand Isle''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] garrison on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Vladet]], the capital of the [[Rachuk sector/Legends|Rachuk sector]]. The base was located inside the crater of an extinct volcano. It was defended by [[Deflector shield/Legends|shield]] generators and two planetary [[Ion cannon/Legends|ion cannons]], but its old [[Wikipedia:Geothermal|geothermal]] power tap was insufficient to power the shields and ion cannons simultaneously. The only other defenses on the ground were four [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE/LN starfighters]], making Grand Isle heavily reliant on the [[Rachuk Sector Fleet]] for protection.

The original role of the base was to discourage [[Pirate/Legends|piracy]] in the sector, but it also became the headquarters of [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Devlia]], the commander of the Rachuk sector Fleet. In [[6 ABY/Legends|6.5 ABY]], Grand Isle was targeted by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] in [[Defense of Vladet|retaliation]] against a [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]] raid that Devlia had sent against [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron's]] base on [[Talasea]]. The [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wings]] of [[Defender Wing]] broke through the north wall of Grand Isle's crater and destroyed the base with [[Proton torpedo/Legends|proton torpedoes]], killing Admiral Devlia.

